title: dentifying a type face
content:

comments.content:
Hi Philip,

you’re posting in the wrong forum; try the [Type ID board](http://web.archive.org/web/20080907013340/http:/typophile.com/forum/29) next time.  
‘Banks’ could have started out as something like [Stymie](http://web.archive.org/web/20080907013340/http:/www.fontshop.com/fonts/singles/linotype/stymie_medium_condensed/?sample_text=Banks&sample_size=96).
